  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37336</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んっ……んん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hnn...Mhmm....</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38068</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうしたの、かぜ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's the matter? Did you catch a cold?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38372</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わかねけど、ちょっと喉の調子が……
……ん、んっん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I dunno, but...My throat feels...tight...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39208</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>体調管理には気をつけないと</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You have to watch out and take care of yourself...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39320</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お〜い、チビ助ぇ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, pipsqueak!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40356</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んだよ！　また、屁掛けようってのか！
その手は二度と喰わねぇぞ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What!? You gonna fart on me or something!?
Well I don't need it coz--!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41276</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こ、これって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wh-What's this?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41704</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もぎたての新鮮なフルーツだでよ。カゼの初期なら
十分なビタミン取って、サッサと寝れば治るだーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Fresh fruits I personally picked. If you take in a lot of vitamins 
and rest before a cold comes in, you'd heal immediately.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42648</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;のために？
……でも、どうして……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You'd do something like that for &lt;Dio&gt;?
But why?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43288</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>細かいこたぁ、どうでもいいだど。
それ食って、とっとと寝れ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh stop worrying about trivial things!
Now, eat this and rest!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44036</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ふふ、悪く言う割に心配してるんだ♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hehe...So you DO worry sometimes.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44860</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_012</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ほら、&lt;Dio&gt;も早くそれ食べて休んだラ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now, why don't you go eat and rest, &lt;Dio&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45460</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_013</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……いや、あの、その……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wait...Uhh...Uhmm...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45692</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_014</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>サ……サンキュー……タン……アルベルト</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Tha...Th-Thank you...Wa--Albert</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_015</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あの子ったら照れちゃって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My, look at how shy he's gotten.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_016</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……アルベルトも優しいところ、
あるんだね！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So you really do have some good in you, Albert!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47532</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_017</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ〜ん？　誰が優しいって？　バカこくでねーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hm? Who's good? Don't talk nonesense!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48120</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_018</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？　だ、だって、あのフルーツって、
&lt;Dio&gt;のために、わざわざ取ってきたんでしょ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? B-But...Surely you didn't just pick those
fruits for &lt;Dio&gt; did you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48540</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_019</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>昨日の食材の残りだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh they're leftovers from yesterday's meal.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48936</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_020</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあ、早く寝ろって、
&lt;Dio&gt;の体調を気遣ってじゃ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then what about the part where you told &lt;Dio&gt; to 
rest immediately? Did you not notice he was unwell?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>49304</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_021</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あいつがカゼ引こうが、おらには関係ねぇだーよ！
&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;に感染ると迷惑だで、サッサと治させたいだけだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't give a slip whether that boy falls sick or not!
I'd prefer that &lt;Mel&gt; doesn't catch a cold from him! Is all!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50220</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_197_022</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;には黙っておかなきゃ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hm...I should keep this a secret from &lt;Dio&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
